= Juli API

Main topic for Juli API is as follows:

* {juli(1) command}[link:files/bin/juli.html]
* Generator(a.k.a. visitor):
  * Juli::Visitor::Html
  * Juli::Visitor::Tree
  * See Juli::Absyn::Visitor how to implement new visitor.
  * See Juli::Visitor::Html::Helper how to implement new helper.
* Parser
  * Juli::Parser      - parse text file
  * Juli::LineParser  - parse line
* Juli::Absyn  - internal representation of input text file.

For general information about juli(1), please see doc/juli(1).txt
(or juli(1).html generated by by juli(1) after installing it).
